name: Janus Greejatus (V)
Lore: 'Imperial council member. Very cruel at heart. Has lusted for power his entire life. Predictable and controllable.',
Text: 'Agendas: logistics, rule. Once per turn, if at Conference Room and you just drew a non-Epic Event destiny < your total Influence here, may use 2 Force to cancel and redraw that destiny or use 4 Force to add 2 to that destiny.',
